MIPS: BMIPS: Fix up Kconfig settings

Factor out common BMIPS options into "CPU_BMIPS".  Add L2 cache for
BMIPS5000.  Add CPU_MIPS32 to satisfy checks in page.h, r4k_switch.S,
tlb-r4k.c, etc.

